	                <p>
	<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-size: 15px;">港府放任白衣黑道無差別攻擊港民，面對謹守工作崗位的記</span><wbr style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" /><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-size: 15px;">者，以及身懷六甲的孕婦，仍以拳腳棍棒相待，失控情況令</span><wbr style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" /><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-size: 15px;">人詫異。黑道成為迫害港民的中共代理人，從「一國兩制」</span><wbr style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" /><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-size: 15px;">轉為「警黑共治」的香港，我們看到中共如何透過一國兩制</span><wbr style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" /><span style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">的糖衣來侵蝕民主自由。</span><br style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" />
	<span style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">　</span><br style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" />
	<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-size: 15px;">在此，民主進步黨除譴責港府放任暴力，同時也將持續努力</span><wbr style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" /><span style="color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">守護台灣民主。</span></p>
